{
  "project": "caspiancoast",
  "label": "Caspian Coast Coffee",
  "description": "Persian café in Venice, California (Los Angeles). The portal edits the LIVE root data files the site actually serves — content.json (homepage + About + shared images/theme), menu.json (menu boards), shop.json (shop) — plus the home FAQ list in content/home.json and the News/Articles collection. Bilingual (English / فارسی) via adjacent _fa-suffixed fields. Edits go straight live; no manual sync.",
